    "By reducing the number of trainable parameters from hundreds of millions to just a few million, these approaches allow companies to deploy specialized models for different languages without the computational overhead of maintaining fully fine-tuned models for each language, making multilingual support more accessible and cost-effective.Enterprise Knowledge Management: A 2024 Together.",
